text:
Dear Ma. Guadalupe, This message is in response to your request to Hope Florida for disaster relief assistance as a result of Hurricane Milton. Based on the information provided, the following community partner(s) may be able to provide services to assist you. Agency: Pathways to Hope by Metropolitan Ministries Website http://www.pinellascounty.org/humanservices/ Contact: Miracles for Pasco Campus - Family Support Center 3216 US-19, Holiday, FL 34691 (813) 209-1000 Services: Toiletries/Personal Hygiene Products Hours: Mon to Fri: 9:00 to 5:00 Should you have any additional needs, please contact us at 833-438-4673. , Hope Florida
